200
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,600
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da će Europska unija propasti do 2030.

201
00:13:19,679 --> 00:13:19,759
[SPEAKER_02] godine.

202
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,879
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da ne može preživjeti.

203
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:21,919
[SPEAKER_02] do 2030.

204
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,080
[SPEAKER_02] godine.

205
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,480
