216
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:54,240
[SPEAKER_02] Volim te zemlje, vole ljude, čvrste i opuštene.

217
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,919
[SPEAKER_02] Zapravo, smiješna priča.

218
