300
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:49,039
[SPEAKER_02] Četrnaest, petnaest, šesnaest godina je upozoravao: Zaustavi se, zaustavi se, zaustavi se, zaustavi se.

301
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:51,279
